snippet.title: Luigi's Lost Levels - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Luigi's Lost Levels is a mod of New Super Luigi U that I've been working on for a few months now. Every level featured in this trailer has been (or will be) made in a timelapse video on this channel, and I'm planning on continuing work on the mod in that same way.
So far this has mostly been a solo project, though @DoctorTricky_ has helped out with some ideas and @B1_Gaming made the mod's logo.
The music in this trailer is the first half of the Super Mario Land Medley from Mario and Sonic at the 2014 Winter Olympics
When will it release? How big will it be? Even I don't know, I'll just be working on the mod till I get sick of it.
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
Hello everyone, Rimea here! 
On this channel I mainly make videos on modding Mario games such as New Super Mario Bros. U or Mario Kart 8 Deluxe and related topics.
